I"ý<p>If your like me your always looking for ways to be notified of things changing in your IT Environment. There are many tools that you can use to help do this. <a href="https://www.statuscake.com">StatusCake</a> is a great free online tool for monitoring website and IP level uptime and downtime with baked in email notifications. <a href="https://www.nagios.org">Zeonoss</a> and <a href="https://www.zenoss.com">NAGIOS</a> are great tools that can offer the same with SNMP Monitoring baked in as well.</p>

